  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Statistics at BEIS
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    We publish statistics on energy, climate change, energy efficiency, fuel poverty, building materials, economic performance and employment, innovation and trade union membership.
  </p>

      
